snippet.textDisplay: Love this style of video ( well, tbh I love all your video's, but super enjoy these style of video's for sure!!) Yes please to more Tati lovely, thank you! Do you know what, I don't ever think I could live in a place that didn't have contrasting seasons, I am in the UK and I love the fact that there are 4 noteable seasons. In fact I don't like how the winters aren't so cold here now, I certainly couldn't live in California that's for sure!! My great Uncle Norman used to live in Seattle ( UK born) and he said that for him it was the closest match for UK weather that he could remember, I miss him & our chats and letter writing!! Anyways I digress, loved the tips and tricks and loving the make up look you had here, it's beautiful! Take care, much love sent from across the pond. xXx 💜💙💜
